data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Introducing a stunning oasis of modern living! Nestled within the picturesque neighborhood of Talavera, this impeccably maintained home boasts timeless elegance and contemporary comforts. With an open and airy floor plan, abundant natural light cascades through large windows all featuring plantation shutters, illuminating the spacious living areas. The gourmet kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's dream, featuring granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and an expansive island perfect for entertaining. The kitchen features a convection oven/ microwave and a built in oven, glass cooktop, and stainless steel exhaust hood. Retreat to the luxurious master suite, complete with a spa-like ensuite bath and a custom California Closet for all your storage needs. Upstairs, a second living room space offers even more room to relax, unwind, and entertain. Here you will also find three spacious bedrooms and another bathroom with jack and jill sinks. Step outside to the screened enclosed lanai, where you can enjoy the serene views of the fenced yard overlooking the tranquil pond and conservation area – a perfect retreat for nature lovers. The meticulously landscaped backyard offers a tranquil escape, while the attached garage and proximity to parks, schools, and shopping make this property the epitome of convenience and style. This seller also has an assumable mortgage to a qualified veteran with a low interest rate. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional residence yours!
